title: DDFP 383: 2015 NFL Season Preview
itunes:title: DDFP 383: 2015 NFL Season Preview
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank and Elliot Harrison to review the court's ruling that nullified Brady's four game suspension and the fallout. They guys then preview the season by asking which teams are the most overhyped, most likely to have the top draft pick next year, most likely to hoist the Lombardi trophy and more. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
